    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant delivers exceptional throttle response via six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been addressed: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The drivetrain utilizes the factory Variable M Differential Lock for precise torque distribution. While the aesthetics show honest patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals remain sharp, making this a robust specimen for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
